items.jobDescribe:
岗位职责：
1、熟悉学校的业务，开展对学校内部招生团队的培训工作，让招生团队成员更加清晰了解学校的各项业务；
2、制定培训及校外宣讲方案，进行招生培训及到校宣讲，推动培训方案落地，完成招生任务;
3、结合招生政策及学校需求，设计开发培训课程，保持课程体系迭代与市场竞争力；
4、协助招生领导处理培训事务，跟踪培训实施效果、参与招生工作总结与反馈；
5、参与围绕招生项目开展的其它工作。
任职资格：
1、本科及以上学历，形象良好，专业不限;
2、具备良好的演讲、人际沟通、招生团队管理、抗压能力，能独立完成培训项目运营相关工作;
3、良好的文案功底，有大型活动组织策划、采编主持、技工院校课程顾问、独立运营招生等经验优先;
4、学习能力强、追求创新，能够迅速适应环境及工作挑战;
5、较强的课程开发能力，具有课程开发经验，熟练使用Office软件、PPT等;

?	Identify training needs, partner with Sales &amp; Operations team to achieve sales objectives and Retail KPI target;
?	Plan and implement the Retail Training calendar, operating plan and budget;
?	Support strategic initiatives designed to drive growth, profitability and customer satisfaction;
?	Responsible for delivering orientation, service &amp; product training course to retail staff, office staff and business partner with professionalism and practical knowledge, and to follow up on training effectiveness;
?	Deliver training courses and coaching to the stores with higher service and skill standards;
?	Provide training logistics like determining the location, time, facilities and training support required for training activities;
?	Follow up training result in store through store visit, telephone communication; 
?	Field coaching in store regularly, submit report to retail team and training team, share the findings with solution and follow up; 
?	Partner with ROMs and Area Supervisors on MSP performance analysis and to develop action plan for improvement; 
?	Dovetailing with the brand strategy plan promoted by the HQ and translating it to the Chinese market on the ground. Responsible for following up the Retail Academy.
